'''Daryne Joshua''' (wavutse 1992), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] .  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''zamamaye cyane Noem My Skollie'' na ''Ellen: Die storie van Ellen Pakkies'' .  Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umugiraneza, umwanditsi, uwashushanyije animasiyo, uwashushanyije amajwi, itangazamakuru n'umuyobozi ushinzwe itumanaho. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i Cape Town. Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Livingstone. Ni umwarimu kuri Sinema n’Ubushakashatsi bwa Sinema muri Cape Peninsula, Kaminuza y’ikoranabuhanga. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka irindwi, yatangiye gukina muri filimi ngufi . Muri kiriya gihe, yakoze no kugurisha imigani mu inshuti ze muri Bridgetown.  Nyuma yaje kwiga muri AFDA, Ishuri ryubukungu bwo guhanga no kubona impamyabumenyi itandukanye.  

Niwe washinze, umwanditsi akaba n'umuyobozi wa Gambit Films yashinze akimara kurangiza. Gambit Films yakoze ikinamico ya mbere ya Afrikaans ya Cape Town, ''Suidooster'' ica kuri DSTV na Kyknet. 

Muri 2016, yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ''Noem My Skollie'' . Filime yatoranijwe nkuwinjiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 89 bya Academy .  Iyi filime yatsindiye ibihembo bya RapidLion kubera amashusho meza na Filime nziza yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo muri 2017. Intsinzi ya firime, yakoze film ye ya kabiri yerekana ''Ellen: Die storie van Ellen Pakkies'' . Byari bishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo ya Ellen Pakkies. Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam (IFFR) ku ya 27 Mutarama 2018 kandi ryishimiwe cyane.    Yasohotse muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo ku ya 7 Nzeri 2018. 

Muri 2018, yanditse inyandiko ya firime ngufi ''nimero 37'' iyobowe na Nosipho Dumisa . Inyandiko yaje gutsindira igihembo cya Afurika yepfo Filime na Televiziyo (SAFTA). 

